Summary: acted more like a cylinder shaped balloon
divs: sighting detailsi noticed a long balloon like object at about 4000 ft nw of the base of haleakala drifting along to the sw. i don't think this was alien but man-made but still unusual and should be noted. photographed w\ a 500mm telephoto, silvery\grey in color, changed shape w\ wind currents. i 1st noticed the object checking summit clouds from my front yard, i thought it was an odd looking object, i've never have seen anything like it before. my feelings were that it was an odd floating object blowing w\ the wind currents till it blew out of sight.
